text: Henry Harold Kennedy Jr. (born February 22, 1948) is an American Senior United States District Judge of the United States District Court for the District of Columbia since 2011. He was nominated to the court in 1997 by President Bill Clinton."Two D.C. Federal Judges to Retire", The BLT, November 10, 2011. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:American judges Category:Politicians from South Carolina Category:Lawyers from South Carolina Category:Politicians from Washington, D.C.
